  "name": "RPlog_The_Reactivation_of_Ambassador_Delgard",
  "title": "A Recruitment in Organa Park",
  "summary": "In the tranquil Organa Park of New Alderaan, the semi-retired ambassador Ambrosia Ad-Delgard watches over her young daughter Gabi and a stampede of other children when she is approached by the newly promoted New Republic Captain Rasi Cen. Rasi has come on business: with the Empire poised to accuse Caspar of aiding the Republic war effort and to extort concessions, he needs Ambrosia to reactivate her old contacts in the Caspian Defense Union and lay groundwork for a looming propaganda war. As they talk, the conversation is punctuated by Gabi skidding into the fastidious officer and a poignant question about her absent father, and by Ambrosia quietly dosing the alloy-replaced joints damaged in a past embassy attack. Ambrosia agrees to reestablish active contact on Caspar, requesting time to arrange a tutor and schooling for Gabi and transportation for them both. Rasi promises a fast civilian ship and a top pilot, welcomes her aboard, and departs.",
